{
  "title": "piyawan no teyhesa ka ili",
  "titleCh": "各村落界線",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "傳統中，各村落的疆界主要是以天然的地形為依據，像是河流或山的稜線。比較特別的是達悟族以海洋為生，因此產生了海域的疆界，此時，海邊的岩石就成為村落疆界的標記。依照傳統規範，族人絕不可越過界線，以避免村落之間的戰爭。",
      "ab": "o adan a iwawalam da no kakoa pa am, amyan so piyawan no mikeyleyli ya, o piyawan da do awa am, rarako a mao, am oyo sira o tovilan da do piyawan no teyhesa ka ili. ji to mangnami o adan a piyawan no ili a mangey pirwahen a piwawakayan, ji to mangnami o piyawan do awa mangey peytawazan, am pamaltogan so among, ta marahet ori a ipey arap no teyhesa ka ili.",
